---
import Breadcrumbs from '../../components/Breadcrumbs.astro'
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---
<Layout title="Book a Call | Rank4AI" description="Book a 30-minute discovery call with Rank4AI. Discuss your AI search visibility and find out how we can help.">
<section class="pt-24 pb-24">
  <div class="max-w
    <Breadcrumbs items={[
      { label: 'Home', href: '/' },
      { label: 'Book A Call' }
    ]} />
-[600px] mx-auto px-10 max-md:px-6 text-center">
    <p class="text-[13px] font-semibold uppercase tracking-[0.1em] text-accent mb-4">Book a Call</p>
    <h1 class="mb-6">Book a Call</h1>

    <img src="/images/content/ai-search-signals.svg" alt="AI search visibility signals" class="w-full rounded-xl mb-8 mt-6" loading="lazy">
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-4">30-minute discovery call to discuss your situation. No obligation, no sales pressure.</p>
    <p class="text-[17px] text-text-muted leading-relaxed mb-10">We will ask about your business, your current visibility, and what you want to achieve. You will leave with a clear understanding of where you stand and what the right next step is.</p>
    <a href="https://calendly.com/rank4ai/rank4aidiscovery" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="cta-primary">Book Your Call on Calendly &rarr;</a>
    <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-text-muted">Or start with a <a href="/free-audit/" class="link">free AI Search Visibility Audit</a> first.</p>
  </div>
</section>
</Layout>
